---

# Philosophy

Creators should spend more time creating and less time managing.

CreativeOS automates repetitive tasks while leaving creative decisions in the hands of the creator.

---

# Features (Planned)

- Project Workspaces
- Song Management
- Book Projects
- AI Prompt Management
- AI Image Workflows
- AI Video Workflows
- Content Calendar
- Campaign Management
- Social Media Planning
- Spotify Promotion
- Analytics Tracking
- Plugin Architecture
- Creator Templates
- CLI Interface

---

# Example Commands

```bash
creativeos init

creativeos doctor

creativeos status

creativeos new-song "No Lose Guard"

creativeos weekly

creativeos generate-prompts

creativeos generate-captions

creativeos analytics
```

